description: Sends feedback to CodeGuru Profiler about whether the anomaly detected by the analysis is useful or not.

parameters.name: anomalyInstanceId
parameters.description: The universally unique identifier (UUID) of the AnomalyInstance object that is included in the analysis data.

parameters.name: profilingGroupName
parameters.description: The name of the profiling group that is associated with the analysis data.

parameters.name: type
parameters.description: The feedback tpye. Thee are two valid values, Positive and Negative.
